\begin_layout Standard
The function 
\begin_inset Formula \[
s_{w}\left(x\right)=\begin{cases}
w^{n} & \mbox{ for }\frac{1}{2^{n+2}}<x<\frac{1}{2^{n+1}}\\
0 & \mbox{ for }x=\frac{1}{2^{n}}\\
s\left(1-x\right) & \mbox{ for }\frac{1}{2}<x\end{cases}\]

